# =============================================================================
#  ForgeOS — Master Environment Example
# =============================================================================
#
#  EVERY API KEY, TOKEN, AND CREDENTIAL THIS OPERATOR MIGHT TOUCH — placeholders
#  only. Copy to ~/.env.forge (chmod 600) and fill in the values you actually
#  use. Source from your shell rc:
#
#      set -a; source ~/.env.forge; set +a
#
#  Each provider block carries its sign-up / dashboard URL above the variable
#  so re-keying after a wipe is a single-click trip per service.
#
#  THIS FILE IS PUBLIC. Never replace placeholders with real values here.
#  See SECURITY.md and AGENTS.md (Public/private boundary).
#
# =============================================================================
#
#  Conventions
#  -----------
#  • Sections are wrapped in box-drawing rules (═══) for visual scan.
#  • Each provider has a comment block:
#        # ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#        # NAME                                  sign-up: https://...
#        # ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  • Multiple env vars per provider when the platform needs more than the key
#    (org id, project id, region, base url, etc).
#  • `# TODO: verify URL` marks providers I was less confident about — confirm
#    the URL before relying on it after a wipe.
#
# =============================================================================



# ╔═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
# ║                  1. FRONTIER LLM APIS (chat completions)                  ║
# ╚═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝


# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# ANTHROPIC                                sign-up: https://console.anthropic.com/
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=https://api.anthropic.com


# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# OPENAI                                   sign-up: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
OPENAI_API_KEY=
OPENAI_ORG_ID=
OPENAI_PROJECT_ID=
OPENAI_BASE_URL=https://api.openai.com/v1


# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# GOOGLE AI STUDIO  (Gemini)               sign-up: https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
